{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0001", "text": "想出去玩嗎 即管去找他 他比我解渴吧", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 3, 4, 9, 3, 3, 9, 4, 9, 3, 3, 9, 5, 9, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["soeng2", "ceot1", "heoi3", "waan2", "maa1", "zik1", "gun2", "heoi3", "zaau2", "taa1", "taa1", "bei2", "ngo5", "gaai2", "hot3", "baa6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "出去玩", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "即管", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "解渴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0002", "text": "但夜來頭痛 會發現你突然 沒有解藥嗎", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 0, 0, 4, 4, 2, 5, 2, 0, 2, 5, 9, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "je6", "loi4", "tau4", "tung3", "faat3", "jin6", "nei5", "dat6", "jin4", "mut6", "jau5", "gaai2", "joek6", "maa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "夜來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "頭痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發現", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "突然", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "解藥", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0003", "text": "他比我新鮮 但是會厭吧 想想過幾個月", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 9, 5, 3, 3, 2, 2, 4, 2, 9, 9, 4, 9, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["taa1", "bei2", "ngo5", "san1", "sin1", "daan6", "si6", "jim3", "baa6", "soeng2", "soeng2", "gwo3", "gei2", "go3", "jyut6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "他", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "新鮮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會厭", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "幾個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "月", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0004", "text": "蜜月期完了 你缺乏我照料 又會安樂嗎", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 0, 0, 5, 5, 4, 2, 5, 4, 2, 2, 3, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mat6", "jyut6", "kei4", "jyun4", "liu5", "nei5", "kyut3", "fat6", "ngo5", "ziu3", "liu6", "jau6", "on1", "lok6", "maa1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "蜜月", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "期完", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "缺乏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "照料", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "又", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "安樂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嗎", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0005", "text": "你約會過某人 我說不要緊", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 4, 5, 0, 5, 4, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "joek3", "gwo3", "mau5", "jan4", "ngo5", "syut3", "bat1", "jiu3", "gan2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "約會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "某人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不要緊", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0006", "text": "你去玩到夠吧 我在這裏等", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 9, 4, 4, 2, 5, 2, 5, 5, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "heoi3", "waan2", "dou3", "gau3", "baa6", "ngo5", "zoi6", "ze5", "leoi5", "dang2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "玩", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "夠", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "等", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0007", "text": "不經過花心 怎麼會安心", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 4, 3, 3, 9, 3, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "ging1", "gwo3", "faa1", "sam1", "zam2", "mo1", "on1", "sam1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "經過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "花心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "安心", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0008", "text": "即管放膽試吧 共萬人狂吻", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 9, 4, 9, 4, 2, 2, 2, 0, 0, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zik1", "gun2", "fong3", "daam2", "si3", "baa6", "gung6", "maan6", "jan4", "kwong4", "man5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "即管", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放膽", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "試", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "共萬人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "狂吻", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0009", "text": "看最後發現誰 是最吸引", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 4, 2, 4, 2, 0, 2, 4, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["hon3", "zeoi3", "hau6", "faat3", "jin6", "seoi4", "si6", "zeoi3", "kap1", "jan5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "看", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發現", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吸引", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0010", "text": "試試換個愛人 我最多要忍一陣", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 4, 2, 4, 4, 0, 5, 4, 3, 4, 9, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["si3", "si3", "wun6", "go3", "oi3", "jan4", "ngo5", "zeoi3", "do1", "jiu3", "jan2", "jat1", "zan6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "試試", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "換個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最多要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "忍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一陣", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0011", "text": "你會求我以後 當沒有發生", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 0, 5, 5, 2, 2, 5, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "kau4", "ngo5", "ji5", "hau6", "mut6", "jau5", "faat3", "sang1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你會求", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "以後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "當", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "發生", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0012", "text": "就是鬥氣不信 我對於你等如別人", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 4, 4, 3, 4, 5, 4, 3, 5, 9, 0, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zau6", "si6", "dau3", "hei3", "bat1", "seon3", "ngo5", "deoi3", "jyu1", "nei5", "dang2", "jyu4", "bit6", "jan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "就是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "鬥氣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "信", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對於", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "等", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0013", "text": "舊了便輸給滿街的飛吻", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 2, 3, 3, 5, 3, 3, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gau6", "liu5", "bin6", "syu1", "kap1", "mun5", "gaai1", "dik1", "fei1", "man5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "舊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "輸給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "滿街", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "飛吻", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0014", "text": "就是放你出去 放你飛上天堂覓尋", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 4, 5, 3, 4, 4, 5, 3, 3, 0, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zau6", "si6", "fong3", "nei5", "ceot1", "heoi3", "fong3", "nei5", "fei1", "tin1", "tong4", "mik6", "cam4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "就是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "出去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "放", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "飛上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天堂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "覓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "尋", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0015", "text": "沒有藥 似我會醫這心癮", "structure": {"line_index": 15, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 2, 5, 5, 3, 5, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mut6", "jau5", "joek6", "ci5", "ngo5", "ji1", "ze5", "sam1", "jan2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "藥", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "似", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "醫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心癮", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "解藥", "artists": ["陳奕迅"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1921", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0014", "next_line_id": "lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_MTkyMQ_0016", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
